name: Glass_2_Door_Tall_Cabinet_with_Drawer
reviews: The box & contents within appear intimidating. However once I set out all the pieces & followed the directions carefully, I was very happy! Nice piece for the money. If you don't like fancy furniture prices, & if you can provide a little elbow grease on your behalf, this may be for you! If you build the cabinet all alone, expect to spend a couple hours, but the time and effort pays off in a really nice piece! :)
description:
Bring a touch of country charm to your home with the Homestar
Accent Cabinet. This cute cabinet exudes cottage style with its
clean lines and simple silhouette. It has double glass doors that
swing open to reveal spacious shelves for storing things like
antique dishes and family heirlooms or books and DVDs. It is made
